&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Think about any ten unconnected things. &lt;br>
Connect them all in a half-page story. &lt;br>
Any human can do this. &lt;br>
Children can do it better and faster.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>A small patch of white clouds in the sky, &lt;br>
a crow in the nest, a snake crawling to cross the road, &lt;br>
a man going to home in his cycle, &lt;br>
the day is Saturday, time is inauspicious Rahukaal, &lt;br>
man listening to a lovely old song from FM radio. &lt;br>
What is the connection between all these? &lt;br>
Who gave meaning to the time that it is good and bad?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>